results.body:
Hej, please always provide basic taxa like animal, plant, insect, fungi or bird to avoid the "unknown"-category, observations can get stuck there - thanks
check out these good tips on how to improve your observations and get the best out of iNaturalist
https://forum.inaturalist.org/t/helpful-tips-and-resources-for-beginner-plant-inatters-and-common-beginner-mistakes/28824
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xENz1xRu0wI&ab_channel=iNaturalist
